Package services.persistence.dao

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IElementDAO
    Interface used for defining methods associated with tournament elements and match, that are implemented in ElementDAOImpl
    IFacade
    Interface for FacadeImpl
    IManagerDAO
    Interface used for defining methods associated with managers, that are implemented in ManagerDAOImpl
    ITeamDAO
    Interface used for defining methods associated with teams, players and stadiums, that are implemented in TeamDAOImpl
    ITournamentDAO
    Interface used for defining methods associated with tournaments, that are implemented in TournamentDAOImpl
